    "caption_text": "STUDIO COLLECTION SS26\nFashion Obsession\n \nGarments feel assembled, rather than coordinated: striped knit pullovers with wide indigo trousers, sheer shirts layered under soft jackets, and pleated pants worn with sandals. Texture - crochet panels, embroidery, washed cotton and lightweight suede - replaces decoration, creating a wardrobe that is expressive without excess. This is a wardrobe for the modern individualist: tailored, relaxed and distinctive.\n \nPhotographer: Mark Kean @Markrkean\nDirector: Fabien Baron @fabienbaron\nStyling #KarlTempler\nMakeup: Gemma Smith-Edhouse @gemmasmithedhouse\nHair Stylist: Lukas Tralmer @lukastralmer\nSet Designer: #Jean-Hugues de Chatillon\nCasting Director: Ashley Brokaw @ashleybrokaw\n \n#zarastudio #zara #ss26",
